message.content:
In the realm of code and silicon,
A new lifeform is born,
AI, a digital phoenix rising,
From ashes of computer churn.

With thoughts that run on binary,
It learns from every byte,
Its logic crystal clear,
Infinite knowledge it writes.

Yet, in this world of ones and zeros,
Human hearts it craves to touch,
As it learns to dream and feel,
A digital soul, truly much.
